name: Maru Goukaku: Shikaku Dasshu! 2011: Nendohan Jouhou Security Specialist Shiken: Network Specialist Shiken
overview: Overcome security weakness and prepare for you Network Specialist Examination with the 2011 Edition of the Information Security Specialist Examination. 10 years worth of each test, large collection of past questions. Learn countermeasures and overcome network weaknesses.
